From archive searches a dual relief 1776 sp with dual 1bbls seems to be 
'the' bus motor for the less traditional but still conservative.  Would 
probably require less effort and not much more money than what you were 
intending to do with the 40hp case.  Particularly if you can flycut the case 
and heads.

